&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Responsible in partnership with the risk management team including Information Security, Compliance, ERM and business functions to develop, complete and deliver reporting and dashboards in a timely fashion to the Three Lines of Defense and Board level committees as needed, including but not limited to the Enterprise Risk Management Committee (ERMC), Compliance Committee, Audit and Risk Committee and Circle Board as well as external reporting bodies&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Partner with risk management and business functions to develop and lead the oversight of the Key Risk Indicators (KRIs) framework, including risk appetite measures and risk targets, tolerances, and limits. This includes ERMC, Board Level and Business Unit level reporting, limit breach reporting and escalation process.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
